precis:
Authority for the Secretary of State for External Affairs:
(a) to sign an Agreement with the Government of the Kingdom of Spain
concerning the employment of dependents of employees of each Government
assigned to official missions in the other country
(b) to execute and issue an Instrument of Full powers authorizing Julie
Loranger or Lorne S. Clark to sign the said Agreement.
